WEBVTT

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.856
Hear her speaking, sparking alarm.

00:03:31.880 --> 00:03:34.776
See her dancing, summoning the dead,

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:36.616
resurrecting new life.

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:39.736
Heaven hears her knocking on the door,

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:43.416
safely transporting the ones
who call for her assistance.

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:47.176
Wild women, they open
portals to new worlds,

00:03:47.200 --> 00:03:50.000
new speech, new dreams.

00:03:50.720 --> 00:03:53.056
Oh, dearly beloveds,

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:56.856
so dearly departed
from the ways of the guardian,

00:03:56.880 --> 00:03:58.456
beware.

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:02.560
For wild women are not to be tamed.